menu "App Shell"

    config APP_SHELL_TASK_STACK_SIZE
        int "App shell task stack size"
        default 6144
        range 3072 16384
        help
            `app_shell` task の stack size です。
            English: this single owner task runs the active foreground app and
            owns `cyd_display`, so its stack must cover the active app step.

    config APP_SHELL_TASK_PRIORITY
        int "App shell task priority"
        default 5
        range 1 24
        help
            `app_shell` task priority です。

endmenu
